<br>
When I was xian, I tried to accept the fact that not everyone went to heaven. I had a very hard time tryingto accept the fact that not everyone I loved would be there, YET every time someone died, I was told they were in heaven. It is a comforting thought to think that you will see your dead relatives again and some people take comfort in knowing that people like Dahmer(sp?) will be in hell. It is something to make life easier to bare.<br>
<br>
(my .02)<br>
